{
  "stem": "4967.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I had a special permit, a [NON-ENGLISH], which stated-- and this [NON-ENGLISH] only good people, tradesman, or people, professional people who were needed for the German's support, like electricians, tradesmen, doctors, or people who worked in the big workshops.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the workshops they produced clothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was big laundries as well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Germans used to bring in laundry to be cleaned from the front or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It used to be repaired and washed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think my sister worked in the [INAUDIBLE] in the laundries-- I'm not sure-- outside the-- outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we used to get special facilities, maybe extra coupon to get an extra piece of bread or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't walk around in the streets, in particular children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We childrens, we children, were the first one to feel that there was something going to be a wrong in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one morning, we woke up six o'clock.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The men went to work, and the ghetto was surrounded by the Germans and Lithuanians.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they went from house to house and picked up women who didn't have work permit, sick people, and children.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was actually an action by the Germans to take out those people, in particular, the children.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my late mother didn't work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My late sister, my late brother, and myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we hide under a staircase.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the first two days were white Russians and Lithuanians searching for sick people, and children, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they didn't find us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The main [? model ?] was to, was to take away from the Jewish people the valuables, maybe even to rape girls.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was a child.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I didn't seen it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And for the [INAUDIBLE], the Germans were not happy.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
